latestPosts.caption:
Happy Birthday to my baby Milo, you are 4 years old today!! 🐾

Although you can’t speak you changed my world 180 degrees 4 years ago. You made me realise love doesn’t need a language, it only needs a soulful connection. Your eyes and gestures speak a 1000 words everyday.

I hope everyone could experience love like this once but unfortunately this kind of love is only reserved for a few blessed ones 

Tu hi mera “ghar” hai 🏠
